post.title: We've moved!
post.content: Today marks another chapter in our story. We've taken lease on a new office. If you're passing, do drop by and say hi. We're now on 27-28 Strand Street Great, Dublin 1. [![IMG_6244](images/IMG_6244.jpg)](https://tapadoo.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/IMG_6244.jpg)
